---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AsciiHover from '../components/AsciiHover.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hair Loss" description="Clinical evaluation and treatment for hair loss. Telehealth across Florida with personalized, evidence-based plans.">

  <section class="pt-40 pb-28 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-36" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a1410 0%, #080808 50%, #141018 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal max-w-3xl">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">Hair Loss</span>
        <h1 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.0] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text mb-8">
          Hair loss doesn't<br />have to be <em class="text-primary italic">permanent</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-text/50 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-[540px] mb-10">
          Evidence-based evaluation and treatment for hair thinning and loss. We identify the cause and build a plan that works.
        </p>
        <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Book a Visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Options -->
  <section class="pb-28 sm:pb-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">Your Options</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">Treatment <em class="text-primary italic">options</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[24px] p-8 sm:p-10 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Medication Therapy</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> FDA-approved options like finasteride and minoxidil</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Dosing tailored to your health profile</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Clear discussion of benefits and side effects</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[24px] p-8 sm:p-10 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Hormonal Evaluation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Lab work to identify underlying hormonal factors</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Thyroid, testosterone, and DHT assessment</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Provider-led results review and next steps</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[24px] p-8 sm:p-10 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Regular check-ins to track progress</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Plan adjustments based on your response</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Long-term support for sustained results</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Causes Hair Loss -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 relative" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a0f0a 0%, #0c0c0c 50%, #0a0f1a 100%);">
    <AsciiHover charset="·×∘" cellSize={24} radius={140} baseOpacity={0.03} />
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text mb-8">
          What causes<br /><em class="text-accent italic">hair loss</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text/40 text-base leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[540px] mx-auto">
          Hair loss is rarely caused by a single factor. Understanding the root cause is the first step to effective treatment.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-left">
          <div class="bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[20px] p-8 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Genetics</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">DHT sensitivity inherited through family, the most common cause of male pattern baldness.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[20px] p-8 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Hormones</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Imbalances in testosterone, thyroid, or other hormones that affect hair growth cycles.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[20px] p-8 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Stress</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Chronic stress and lifestyle factors that push hair follicles into a resting phase.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[20px] p-8 hover:border-[#3AABA5]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Nutrition</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Deficiencies in iron, zinc, biotin, and other nutrients essential for healthy hair.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">Common Questions</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">What to <em class="text-primary italic">know</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        {[
          { q: 'What causes male pattern hair loss?', a: 'Male pattern hair loss is primarily driven by genetics and DHT — a hormone derived from testosterone. It causes hair follicles to shrink over time, leading to thinner hair and eventual loss in predictable patterns.' },
          { q: 'Are the medications safe?', a: 'Finasteride and minoxidil are both FDA-approved with well-established safety profiles. Your provider will review your health history and discuss potential side effects so you can make an informed decision.' },
          { q: 'How long until I see results?', a: 'Most patients begin noticing changes within 3 to 6 months of consistent treatment. Hair growth is gradual, and your provider will monitor progress and adjust your plan as needed.' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <details class="reveal group bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-[rgba(237,233,224,0.1)] rounded-[20px]">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 sm:px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer text-text font-display font-light text-lg sm:text-xl">
              {item.q}
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-5 sm:px-6 pb-5 text-text/50 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">{item.a}</div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-36 sm:py-44 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f1a14 0%, #0c0c0c 50%, #1a0f14 100%);">
    <AsciiHover charset="·+×∘⊹" radius={200} baseOpacity={0.03} />
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 text-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.0] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text mb-8">
          Start your<br /><em class="text-primary italic">evaluation</em> today
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text/50 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[580px] mx-auto">
          Get a clear understanding of what's causing your hair loss and a plan built around your goals.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Book a Visit</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-pill btn-outline">Ask a Question</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach((e) => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); }); }, { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>
<style>
  .btn-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-ui, 'Inter', sans-serif);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 48px;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 228, 224, 0.2);
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
